  <description>
    <p>
      Videomass is a powerful, multitasking and cross-platform graphical user
      interface (GUI) for FFmpeg and yt-dlp. It offers a wide range of features
      and functions, making it a comprehensive software solution.
    </p>
    <p>
      Videomass is written in Python3 using the wxPython-Phoenix GUI toolkit.
    </p>
